  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q105",
  "body": "What do we pray for in the fifth petition?\n\nIn the fifth petition, which is, 'And forgive us our debts, as we forgive our debtors,' we pray, That God, for Christ's sake, would freely pardon all our sins; which we are the rather encouraged to ask, because by his grace we are enabled from the heart to forgive others.",
